---
title: Spiced Chickpeas, Tofu and Spinach with Fluffy Cilantro Rice and Yogurt Sauce
description: This vegetarian supper is packed with chickpeas, tofu and Indian-style spices. Fluffy rice is the perfect base for this curry and cooling yogurt brings it all together!
